@startuml
title Patron Decorator - Proteccion de vistas de pedidos

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Admin" as Admin

rectangle "Peticion HTTP" as Request
rectangle "never_cache" as NeverCache
rectangle "ensure_csrf_cookie" as Csrf
rectangle "login_required" as Login
rectangle "user_passes_test(is_admin_user)" as Role
rectangle "create_order()\nupdate_order()\ndelete_order()" as View
database "Modelos y formularios" as Models

Admin --> Request
Request --> NeverCache
NeverCache --> Csrf
Csrf --> Login
Login --> Role
Role --> View
View --> Models

note right of Login
GoF Decorator:
cada decorador agrega una responsabilidad
sin cambiar el cuerpo de la vista.
end note

note bottom of Role
Autenticacion, autorizacion,
CSRF y cache quedan separados
del flujo de negocio.
end note

@enduml
